messages.content: how to contac facebook business suite via email

There is no direct email address to contact Facebook Business Suite. Support is handled through the platform itself. You can access it by:

1.  Going to business.facebook.com, clicking "Help" and then "contact support".
2.  Through Facebook Ads Manager, by clicking the question mark icon and selecting "contact support team".

These options may lead to live chat or email support.

messages.content: can you send live support url?

There isn't a direct URL for Facebook's live support. You have to be logged into your account to access it.

You can start by going to the Meta Business Suite here:

[https://business.facebook.com/](https://business.facebook.com/)

Once you are logged in, look for the "Help" or question mark icon to find the "contact support" option. This will lead you to their available support channels, which often includes live chat.
